ce src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642570/extras/4b073d56b9c4b7dd3f9583ac05859b52.webm?t=1774342202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642570/extras/4b073d56b9c4b7dd3f9583ac05859b52.mp4?t=1774342202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642570/extras/019fa1c5cd70b8943c92168993982581.avif?t=1774342202\" width=616 height=94 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every region in Lonkata has its warden Boss. They have their identical skills, which requires adaptable use of your marbles. Ice for slow and Fire for ignite, don't forget the Regen marble that can heal your HP. Exploit your surroundings with flexible positioning. Terminate all threats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642570/extras/9f51ec4261e72b3f787e2f8196873f6b.poster.avif?t=1774342202\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642570/extras/9f51ec4261e72b3f787e2f8196873f6b.webm?t=1774342202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642570/extras/9f51ec4261e72b3f787e2f8196873f6b.mp4?t=1774342202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642570/extras/b5f69c3f1b1a4c48ed21610f98e2b527.avif?t=1774342202\" width=616 height=94 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story happens in a Ultra-Capitalism city called Lonkata, where 